890
01:33:44,880 --> 01:33:45,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo, ono.

891
01:33:45,760 --> 01:33:46,239
[SPEAKER_00] Hajde vi.

892
01:33:46,800 --> 01:33:46,880
[SPEAKER_00] Sada.

893
01:33:47,439 --> 01:33:48,560
[SPEAKER_00] Osoba i normalno.

894
01:33:49,359 --> 01:33:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] Izglasaju ujedinjenim nacijama.

895
01:33:52,079 --> 01:33:53,840
[SPEAKER_00] I vječu sigurnosti izglasaju.

896
01:33:54,159 --> 01:33:56,399
[SPEAKER_00] I onda Amerika, NATO i ovi svi.

897
01:33:56,640 --> 01:33:57,439
[SPEAKER_00] I oni napadnu.

898
01:33:57,600 --> 01:33:59,680
[SPEAKER_00] Donese se odluka da napadnu Irak.

899
01:34:00,960 --> 01:34:04,399
[SPEAKER_00] E sad je tu bio isto Bush.

900
01:34:04,560 --> 01:34:05,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ali stariji Bush je bio.

901
01:34:05,920 --> 01:34:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] A ne drugi Bush.

902
01:34:07,279 --> 01:34:08,640
[SPEAKER_00] Jer isto se zovu i stariji.

903
01:34:09,840 --> 01:34:10,800
[SPEAKER_00] Senior i junior.

904
01:34:10,960 --> 01:34:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

905
01:34:11,680 --> 01:34:12,239
[SPEAKER_00] Pate je bio.

906
01:34:12,239 --> 01:34:14,800
